In the MATTER OF DISCIPLINE OF Lewis P. HANNAH, III No. D-3059 Supreme Court of the United States. February 24, 2020

Lewis P. Hannah, III, of Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring *1257him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
